astroberry64-server-wui (2.0.9-astroberry64.5) trixie; urgency=medium

  * Replace RealVNC Server with x11vnc for noVNC compatibility
  * RealVNC proprietary protocol incompatible with web-based noVNC client
  * Configure lightdm for X11 (Wayland incompatible with VNC screen sharing)
  * Set VNC password to 'astrober' (8-character VNC protocol limit)
  * Web-based desktop access now functional for field astronomy use

 -- Astroberry64 Team <astroberry64@speckle.red>  Tue, 08 Oct 2025 19:30:00 +0200

